events.name: Penn State Nittany Lions at Illinois Fighting Illini

headlines.description: Miles Sanders set career highs by rushing for 200 yards and three touchdowns, Trace McSorley threw for three TDs and ran for a personal-best 92 yards, and No. 10 Penn State scored 35 points in the fourth quarter to pull away for a 63-24 victory over...
headlines.shortLinkText: Sanders, McSorley lead No. 10 Penn State over Illinois 63-24

video.headline: Sanders runs all over Illini defense

events.name: Florida Atlantic Owls at UCF Knights

headlines.description: McKenzie Milton ran for a career-best three touchdowns while throwing for three more, helping No. 16 UCF extend the nation's longest winning streak with a 56-36 rout of Florida Atlantic on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Milton accounts for 6 TDs, No. 16 UCF routs FAU 56-36

events.name: Washington State Cougars at USC Trojans

headlines.description: J.T. Daniels passed for 241 yards and three touchdowns, and Jay Tufele blocked Washington State's attempt at a tying field goal with 1:41 to play in Southern California's 18th consecutive home victory, 39-36 Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: USC beats Wash St 39-36 on Daniels' 3 TDs, Tufele's block

video.headline: USC blocks Washington St.'s game-tying FG
